import { useEffect, useContext, useState } from "react"; import TopNav from "../../topNav/js/topNav"; import "../css/longs.css"; import { UseContextValues } from "../../../App"; import shortenNumber from "../../shortenNumber"; export default function LongsComp() { const videoInfo = useContext(UseContextValues); const [uryFirstVideo, setUryFirstVideo] = useState({}); const [urySecondVideo, setUrySecondVideo] = useState({}); const [urySubs, setUrySubs] = useState({}); const [beterVideo, setBeterVideo] = useState({}); const [beterSubs, setBeterSubs] = useState({}); useEffect(() => { console.log(videoInfo); setUryFirstVideo(videoInfo.uryFirstVideo); setUrySecondVideo(videoInfo.urySecondVideo); setUrySubs(videoInfo.urySubs); setBeterVideo(videoInfo.beterVideo); setBeterSubs(videoInfo.beterSubs); },[videoInfo.fetchingResult]) setTimeout(() => {console.log(shortenNumber(urySubs.subscribers))},1000) return (
{urySecondVideo.views}
{urySecondVideo.likes}
{urySubs.subscribers} subscribers
{uryFirstVideo.views}
{uryFirstVideo.likes}
{urySubs.subscribers} subscribers
{beterVideo.views}
{beterVideo.likes}
{beterSubs.subscribers} subscribers
); }
